com.k2.Wiget

Interface ContainedWiget<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - The output type of the contained wigets
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssembledWiget, ContainerBinding

    public interface ContainedWiget<O>
    The contained wiget interface groups together assembled wigets and container bindings under a single type thus allowing them both to be included in a single list.
    Author:
    simon
